## ── pnpm workspace config ────────────────────────────────────────
## electron-builder + electron-updater require transitive deps
## (builder-util-runtime, fs-extra, etc.) to be resolvable from
## the package's local node_modules. pnpm's strict isolation hides
## them by default. shamefully-hoist makes all deps accessible
## like npm/yarn classic — required for Electron packaging.
shamefully-hoist=true
